---
title: Garlicky Haloumi & Chicken Freekeh Bowl with Cucumber Salsa & Aioli
description: The Mediterranean has some very fresh dishes that leave you feeling relaxed and rejuvenated. We’re taking a page out of their recipe book and creating a freekeh bowl studded with pitted olives, topped with zesty seared chicken and a cooling aioli for that pop of garlic we know and love.

*We’ve replaced the white turnip in this recipe with tomato
due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66590c7378e74cab710b2967-bcf09395.jpeg
